Source: libxxf86dga
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), libxvmc-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://xorg.freedesktop.org/

Package: libxxf86dga
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: X11 Direct Graphics Access extension library
 This package provides libXxf86dga, a shared library which contains 
 X11 direct graphics access routines.

Package: libxxf86dga-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libxvmc-dev, libxxf86dga (= ${binary:Version})
Description: libXxf86dga development headers and static libraries
 This package provides the libXxf86dga static library, pkgconfig data 
 and header files required for developing applications which use 
 libXxf86dga routines.

Package: libxxf86dga-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db, libxxf86dga (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for libXxf86dga
 This package provides man pages for the library routines 
 provided by libXxf86dga.
